BT 1 0 0 1 0 102.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL .719812 Tw (Common outcomes include actions executed without proper context \227 the system acts on the conditions it) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.20148 Tw (was given, not the conditions that actually apply at the moment of action. Escalation of system behaviour) Tj T* 0 Tw .581906 Tw (follows, as the system continues expanding its operations beyond what was originally intended, without any) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.531605 Tw (control point to recognise that a boundary has been crossed. Inability to intervene quickly emerges as a) Tj T* 0 Tw .050379 Tw (consequence \227 because there is no authority validation layer to trigger intervention before harm occurs. And) Tj T* 0 Tw -0.020666 Tw (unclear responsibility for outcomes becomes the operational norm, because the chain of authority from action) Tj T* 0 Tw (back to human decision is too attenuated to reconstruct with confidence.) Tj T* ET
