BT 1 0 0 1 0 54.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL .203263 Tw (Automation changes how systems operate. It does not change the requirement for accountability. The speed) Tj T* 0 Tw .090984 Tw (at which a system acts, the scale at which it operates, and the complexity of the processes it executes are all) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.221799 Tw (properties of the technology. Accountability is a property of governance. Technology does not resolve the) Tj T* 0 Tw (accountability requirement \227 it intensifies it.) Tj T* ET
