BT 1 0 0 1 0 102.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL 2.243049 Tw (Systems must remain accountable to human authority \227 traceable to a specific person whose current) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.135574 Tw (conditions support the action being taken. They must be interruptible at critical points \227 capable of being) Tj T* 0 Tw .745783 Tw (stopped when authority cannot be confirmed, rather than defaulting to continuation under uncertainty. They) Tj T* 0 Tw .353227 Tw (must be constrained by defined boundaries \227 scope, context, duration, and consequence, outside which no) Tj T* 0 Tw 3.150299 Tw (action is permitted regardless of capability. And they must remain aligned with real-world impact \227) Tj T* 0 Tw .717279 Tw (recognising that the purpose of authority governance is not procedural compliance but the protection of the) Tj T* 0 Tw (people and systems that automated decisions affect.) Tj T* ET
