BT 1 0 0 1 0 38.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL .729569 Tw (The core principle is simple. If an action carries consequence, it must carry authority. If authority is absent,) Tj T* 0 Tw -0.071227 Tw (control is absent. And where control is absent, risk increases \227 not as a theoretical concern, but as a present) Tj T* 0 Tw (condition accumulating in every system that acts without validating, at execution, that it has the right to act.) Tj T* ET
